All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
Database
Database containing Student list, Faculty list, Project list and FYPCoordinator list.
EnumMatcher
A class that matches enum objects with their corresponding values in the data files.
Excel
A helper class that can read in and store details about the model classes Student, Faculty, FYPCoordinator, Project and Request from data files.
ExcelType
An enumerated class that represents the type of model class in a data file.
FacultyController
A controller class that acts as a "middle man" between the view classes FacultyView, FYPCoordinatorView, LoginView and the model class Faculty.
FacultyStatus
An enumerated class that represents the status of a Faculty in regards to availability of supervising projects.
FYPCoordinatorController
A controller class that acts as a "middle man" between the view classes FYPCoordinatorView, LoginView and the model class FYPCoordinator.
MainApp
Main application for the Final Year Project Portal.
OptionChecker
A helper class that checks whether a user's input is valid.
ProjectController
A controller class that acts as a "middle man" between the view classes FacultyView, FYPCoordinatorView, StudentView and the model class Project.
ProjectStatus
An enumerated class that represents the status of a Project.
RequestController
A controller class that acts as a "middle man" between the view classes FacultyView, FYPCoordinatorView, StudentView and the model classes Request, StudentToSupervisor, StudentToFYPCoor, FacultyToFYPCoor.
RequestStatus
An enumerated class that represents the status of a Request.
RequestType
An enumerated class that represents the type of Request made.
StudentController
A controller class that acts as a "middle man" between the view classes StudentView, FYPCoordinatorView, LoginView and the model class Student.
StudentStatus
An enumerated class that represents the status of a Student in regards to project allocation.
UserController<T>
A controller class that acts as a "middle man" between the view classes UserView, LoginView and the model class User.
UserType
An enumerated class that represents the type of User entering the FYP Portal.
